Definition: usually expressed as `in behalf' rather than `on behalf' and usually with a possessive)
Example: in your behalf; campaigning in his own behalf; spoke a good word in his friend's behalf
Synonyms: sake, for, someone, s, benefit, usually, expressed, as, in, rather, than, on, and, with, a, possessive, your, campaigning, his, own, spoke, good, word, friend
Category: noun.attribute
